abstract: NFL Roundup; New Orleans Saints injured quarterback Drew Brees is expected to return as starter in team's upcoming game against Dallas Cowboys; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Brees missed the Saints’ loss in Carolina last Sunday because of a bruised rotator cuff in his right shoulder. If he does start as planned, he will return to a team that is in desperate need of a victory.

headline.main: Drew Brees Expected to Return for Saints’ Game Against Cowboys
